

     
      "One thing."  He holds up a plastic cricket.  "For when you really  really  need me."  He squeezes it and it makes a *click* sound.  "One click," he says, "is answered by two clicks."  He squeezes it again. *click*click*  "Click once, and I'll answer.  Please, use it sparingly."  He hands it to you.  "Be careful.  I think Hell  and  Heaven are out to get you...."  *smirk*
     
    
